{"tid":878002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[認真post] 中美貿易戰底下，美國到底有咩損失？","createTime":"2018-10-26T18:39:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T06:05:15.000Z","uid":52658,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"72c17becb6895a3eeede801a696a1f078a997ac9","tid":878002,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T18:39:47.000Z","msg":"D新聞 一直以黎都講緊中國點樣被貿易戰影響<br />\n股市又跌 物價又升 <br />\n高科技行業點樣負債倒閉 點點點<br />\n但好少新聞講美國果邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n美國係咪真係完全無穿無爛 當中國狗咁撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但如果貿易戰對美國真係零影響<br />\n做乜要等到今時今日先打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a0cdcaaabf0e62ac2e3f15ab7c2facdbce2ac60","tid":878002,"uid":52658,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T18:44:24.000Z","msg":"美國其實有咩損失可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例如糧食 <br />\n美國將原本供應比中國d貨散晒去歐盟同南美洲<br />\n然後再同巴西打籠通 <br />\n等中國用貴幾倍既價錢買返呢批糧食返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而高科技產業例如晶片 半導體呢d<br />\n對中國出口既份額一直都唔多<br />\n反而中國就要靠美國 歐盟同日本既技術"},{"pid":"470ca1d5c935579cbc5427ca86f3d3b4f932cba4","tid":878002,"uid":52658,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T19:04:39.000Z","msg":"個重點而家中國唔止係同美國打緊<br />\n而家個形勢係中國一個挑晒美國 加拿大 歐盟 日本同澳洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nD黨媒仲日日係度吹奏中國係贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n贏左係邊都未知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n認真post無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p